long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Trustpilot lists data from the search page to a XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Trustpilot listing page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple listing pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export listing data to a xls/csv file, data include: Business Unit Id, Categories, Email, Phone, Website, Display Name, Identifying Name, Is Recommended In Categories, Address, City, Country, Zip Code, Logo Url, Number Of Reviews, Stars, Trust Score, Origin Search Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Trustpilot List Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Trustpilot❗️🔒
